description:
In control of a little girl, get you duckbill back. But watch out, he might bite.
Arrow keys to move;
Q to catch a weakened enemy;
W to jump;
E to normal attack (must have ammo);
1,2,3 to select other caught animals.
-----------------
For now, there is just one enemy in the game. The art for the other enemies is already done but the code is yet under development (fixing major bugs...). There will be a duckbill boss too.
This is an preview of the game mechanisms. All enemies will be catchable and each will give the player habilities and disadvantages. An example is the ladybug that will explode as she touches the ground, sending the player flying a long distance, at cost of life. Other example is the electric eel, the alows a long ranged whip-like attack, but paralyzes the player form time to time. There's 7 kinds of enemies, plus bosses.
We hope to finish the game within the 14 days of avaliation, but you can already play this prototipe and please, give us the feedback.
